Note about foundation.min.js - 5.4.6

Line 1974 was changed form:
self.S(this).trigger('closed').trigger('closed.fndtn.dropdown', [dropdown]);

to:
self.S(this).trigger('closed.fndtn.dropdown', [dropdown]);

This was done to solve an issue with dropdowns in reveal modals (OAM-448 - see: https://github.com/zurb/foundation/issues/4576 )If you update / change this file please note this.

This was changed in the latest version of foundation (as of today), so if this is updated to the latest version please disregard this notice.